Module io.jstach.rainbowgum
Package io.jstach.rainbowgum.spi

Interface RainbowGumServiceProvider.RainbowGumEagerLoad

All Superinterfaces:
RainbowGumServiceProvider
Enclosing interface:
RainbowGumServiceProvider
public static non-sealed interface RainbowGumServiceProvider.RainbowGumEagerLoad extends RainbowGumServiceProvider
This is a marker interface that indicates that a facade implementation will do the eager loading of RainbowGum. This is used to determine if another facade that has the option to queue should queue and not load rainbowgum if any implementations are found of this interface.
See Also:
  • exists()
API Note
Only facade implementers need concern themselves with this interface and for others it is an internal detail.
